3 get_edges test

gv2 <- get_edges(clustirr_output_v2)
nodes <- data.frame(id = 1:5)
nodes$title <- nodes$id
edges <- data.frame(from = gv2$from_ID, to = gv2$to_ID)

visNetwork(nodes, edges)
